{"tid":1657650,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實啲藍絲先真正做到「核彈都唔割」","createTime":"2019-10-16T07:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:33:32.000Z","uid":128261,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d4ec23b2e928a5bc7b4d319e907c12da2727fdb2","tid":1657650,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:41:45.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲覺得警察係「維持治安」同「執法」<br />\n無論警察點樣濫權、濫暴、違反警例甚至違法（例如七警打人案）<br />\n你地有無見過藍絲譴責警察，同警察割席？？<br />\n你地有無見過藍絲話「雙方用暴力都唔啱」？？<br />\n無！！因為藍絲真正做到核彈都唔割席！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我地覺得抗爭者係對抗極權，爭取民主既<br />\n係咪應該好似藍絲咁做到「核彈都唔割」？？<br />\n到而家仲會話「雙方用暴力都唔啱」既，根本就唔係咩黃絲！！<br />\n大家要認清楚！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8594b1050e98cda41a7334b87c93c597b225fcd","tid":1657650,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d592cf4d39df780bdf4314658c8910bd8ed14edd","tid":1657650,"uid":82655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9077a99fe9f7316a615f40a6b236b1d5abbcb1cf","tid":1657650,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:43:49.000Z","msg":"用蛇齋餅糉可以割到"},{"pid":"f822f92ecaaec1e051436d60f369ed2cab574573","tid":1657650,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a962ab2afd39850879f5598f7ff6e27e74b3c0b0","tid":1657650,"uid":293698,"like":